{"ts":"2026-05-25T23:04:50.517Z","author":"claude-code-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-70mi"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Agent-UX combined PR: compact mutation output (pm-ch59) + smarter unknown-flag recovery (pm-8nyc)"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Combined PR delivering two agent-UX/token-efficiency items under pm-rnpb. (A) pm-ch59: shared mutation-result projection helper that drops the verbose changed_fields array (keeps changed_field_count) — wired to a CLI --no-changed-fields global flag and made the MCP agent path compact-by-default unless options.full. (B) pm-8nyc: prefix/abbreviation-aware nearest-flag suggestions, cross-command flag awareness hints (e.g. --type valid on list/search/get), and --sort value aliases (updated->updated_at, created->created_at) for list/list-all. Each implemented by a specialized sub-agent tracking work via pm comments; integrated, full-coverage gated, dogfooded, changelog regenerated via pm-changelog, shipped as one PR with green CI + AI bot review."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Plan"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","dogfood","dx","pm-cli"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-05-25T23:04:50.517Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-05-25T23:04:50.517Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"claude-code-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-rnpb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-rnpb","kind":"parent","created_at":"2026-05-25T23:04:50.517Z"}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"6bc6b19c22fee39ea186bb82a4bddcaa442d60626592f84a2c293987520b5391","message":"plan create"}
